{"tid":2122143,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝你","createTime":"2020-07-23T20:50:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T06:35:32.000Z","uid":254376,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"81c5f4fca35f75c77eaecd6aea9739ee681581c5","tid":2122143,"uid":254376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T20:50:44.000Z","msg":"成個中學生涯都係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺學校每一個角落都有我同你走過既剪影<br />\n喺旺角街道印有我地既足跡<br />\n你教識我好多嘢，令到我成長左好多<br />\n今日你話已經好攰了，今次唔再留你喇<br />\n係你教識我應該要為所愛既人著想<br />\n今次唔再係你拋棄我，係我放你走<br />\n我會學點樣放低你<br />\n多謝你一直以黎對我既所有嘢<br />\n有機會我地再一齊面對呢個荒謬既世界<br />\n我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b2d4ed8d33b75324ddba7dd4c630c273d0e59a1","tid":2122143,"uid":197005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T20:52:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2abfbe90e2e9b13bc0bbb269aeaa39359989b94","tid":2122143,"uid":254376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b2d4ed8d33b75324ddba7dd4c630c273d0e59a1","tid":2122143,"uid":197005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T20:52:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T20:53:58.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6b36dfbcd67d7f7dc66cd4fc5c4a2c1b9341ee","tid":2122143,"uid":336942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T20:54:56.000Z","msg":"加油🤣"},{"pid":"921ab70e6da1e4ee48eff8506fb413dacd1dae80","tid":2122143,"uid":254376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T20:59:25.000Z","msg":"希望你以後可以過得更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b08b376647c24bd1723f108ea64896fea305784","tid":2122143,"uid":140937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T21:17:18.000Z","msg":"加油⋯你起個次出po個陣我就follow左你，<br />\n見到你宜家放低左，<br />\n我都有啲眼濕濕。<br />\n<br />\n我個陣都係岩岩散，<br />\nEx嘅影子周不時都會出現，<br /